haddrill richard m  the wall street transcript richard m haddrill richard m haddrill is chief executive officer of manhattan associates inc a seasoned veteran with more than  years of leadership experience in the software and technology industries since joining manhattan associates in october  mr haddrill has been instrumental in driving a strategic reorganization of the company which has resulted in improved new product delivery enhanced customer orientation profitable expansion into international markets record operational and financial performance and a tenfold increase in the share price at a time when other industry stocks have declined before joining manhattan associates mr haddrill was president and chief executive officer of powerhouse technologies a nasdaqlisted technology provider to the gaming industry he joined powerhouse in  as the company’s executive vice president and was later promoted to president and chief executive officer in  where he engineered a successful turnaround and a near sixfold increase in the share price in three years he received his bachelor of science degree in business from the university of michigan in  he has been active in a variety of civic and charitable organizations including junior achievement the boy scouts of america and various arts and technology organizations mr haddrill also serves as a board member of danka business systems a publicly traded office technology company with revenues exceeding  billion and alliance gaming a nyselisted company providing technology to the gaming industry and outlooksoft a venturebacked business intelligence company related interviewsrichard haddrill  manhattan associates inc manhmay  richard haddrill  manhattan associates manhapril  richard haddrill  manhattan associates inc manhjune  richard haddrill  manhattan associates inc manhmay  richard haddrill  manhattan associates inc manhapril  richard haddrill  manhattan associates inc manhapril  richard m haddrill  powerhouse technologies pwr